<i>noun</i>: 행패 [행패], 비행 [비ː행], 비행 [비ː행], 경범죄 [경범쬐/경범쮀] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>행패 [행패]</dt><br>
<dd>violence; misconduct; misdeed; misdemeanor</dd><br>
<dd>버릇이 없고 도리에 어긋나는 난폭한 말이나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>A rude, violent word or action that contradicts moral standards.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비행 [비ː행]</dt><br>
<dd>wrongdoing; misconduct; misdemeanor; delinquency; malpractice</dd><br>
<dd>도덕이나 규범에서 벗어나는 잘못된 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>A wrong act that goes against morals or norms.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비행 [비ː행]</dt><br>
<dd>wrongdoing; misconduct; misdemeanor; delinquency; malpractice</dd><br>
<dd>도덕에 어긋나는 나쁜 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>A misbehavior that is contrary to morals.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경범죄 [경범쬐/경범쮀]</dt><br>
<dd>misdemeanor; minor offense</dd><br>
<dd>일상생활에서 흔하게 일어나는, 처벌이 가벼운 범죄.</dd><br>
<dd>A crime that occurs often in every day life and which is punished lightly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>